SUMMARY:Get Funded: Grant Application Fundamentals
DESCRIPTION:Discover what grant reviewers are actually looking for\, how to craft applications that rise to the top\, and where to find funding opportunities you didn’t even know existed. You’ll learn the anatomy of a winning application\, the common mistakes that sink strong proposals\, and insider strategies for matching your mission to the right funders. Whether you’ve been rejected before or you’re starting from scratch\, this workshop will transform how you approach grants. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
