SUMMARY:Organic Lawn Renovation & Management
DESCRIPTION:Love your lawn but don’t love all the lawn chemicals? \nJoin Rutgers Master Gardener Brian Monaghan to learn how you can have a beautiful\, healthy\, organic lawn without breaking the bank or your back. \nLearn how to:\n💵Reduce costs\n☣️Eliminate toxins\n🌱Improve soil health and turf vigor\n🐕Make your yard safe for pets & kids \nBring your questions! \nAbout the speaker:\nBrian Monaghan is an organic lawncare expert who has given nearly 100 presentations on the topic on behalf of the Rutgers Master Gardener Speakers Bureau. He has been a Master Gardener for 13 years\, and is active on the Environmental Commission\, the Shade Tree Management Board\, the Community Garden Commission\, and the Open Space Recreation and Conservation Advisory Committee in his hometown of Madison\, NJ. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/organic-lawn-renovation-management/
LOCATION:Glen Ridge Train Station\, 228 Ridgewood Ave\, cor. Bloomfield Ave\, Glen Ridge\, NJ\, 07028\, United States
CATEGORIES:General Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/Organic-Lawn-Care-2.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Glen Ridge Environmental Advisory Committee":MAILTO:goglenridgegreen@gmail.com
