SUMMARY:Loopwell Screening of The (M) Factor 2: Before The Pause | Perimenopause
DESCRIPTION:Join Loopwell for an intimate red carpet premiere screening of The (M) Factor 2: Before The Pause | Perimenopause — a powerful documentary exploring the often-overlooked transitional years leading up to menopause.\nThis NJ premiere will be followed by a fireside chat and Q&A with the film’s executive producers and Loopwell’s founder. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
