SUMMARY:Nidra Nights - A Journey to Deep Restoration
DESCRIPTION:Nidra Nights invites you to let go\, release and immerse yourself in deep relaxation. \nIn this monthly offering\, you’ll practice a 40-45 minute Yoga Nidra guided meditation\, known for delivering the restorative effects of deep rest – similar to 3 hours of sleep – while your mind stays consciously engaged.\nEvery session will offer a unique combination of elements\, which may include gentle movement\, journaling\, personal affirmation work\, or other practices to help ground and center you. Each class provides a different way to experience rest and renewal\, offering a chance to pause and recharge in a meaningful way. \nJoin us in person or online \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/nidra-nights-a-journey-to-deep-restoration/
