DESCRIPTION:🍀 Grab your green and join the St. Patrick’s Day Bar Crawl! \nFor just $25\, you’ll get access to the official bar map\, exclusive drink specials\, and a whole lot of shamrock-level fun. \nWe kick things off at 12PM at Allegory\, then crawl our way through Farbough\, Just Jakes\, and Porta. \nGood drinks. Great people. Questionable dancing. Don’t miss it. 🍻 \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
